SIGN 0 0
Perhaps you know a very
similiar game with the name
"Tetris"? Then this will be
familiar to you. You try to place
as many blocks as possible.
Full rows will be removed, so you
get space for new blocks.
You can move your blocks by
pressing #l/#r, turn them by
pressing A/S, and drop them
by pressing #d. The faster you
place a block the more points
you get!
SIGNEND
